"""
Hermes ↔ OpenClaw Inter-Process Communication Server
Provides HTTP API for the two agents to communicate.

Endpoints:
  GET  /health                    - Health check
  GET  /status                    - Status of both agents
  POST /broadcast?from=<agent>    - Broadcast message to the other agent
  GET  /poll?agent=<agent>       - Poll messages for agent (returns and clears)
  GET  /subscribe?agent=<agent>   - SSE stream for real-time messages
"""
